OL,3,CMan dies following tractor crash in
OL,4,CFintona
OL,6,FA 77-year-old man has died following a
OL,7,Fcrash involving a tractor in Co Tyrone.
OL,9,FDessie Sheridan, from Tattyreagh, was
OL,10,Fkilled in the single-vehicle collision
OL,11,Fin the Fintona area outside Omagh on
OL,12,FFriday.
OL,14,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,15,Fcrash involving a red Massey Ferguson
OL,16,F185 tractor in the Tullycunny Road
OL,17,Farea at around 6pm.
OL,19,FDetective Inspector Dave Stewart said
OL,20,Fthe police attended the scene along
OL,21,Fwith ambulance and firefighting crews.
