OL,6,FHe said: "Sadly, Mr Sheridan was
OL,7,Fpronounced deceased at the scene."
OL,9,FThe Tullycunny Road will remain closed
OL,10,Ffor most of Saturday.
OL,12,FEnquiries are ongoing and police
OL,13,Fappealed for any witnesses, or anyone
OL,14,Fwith information that could assist
OL,15,Fofficers, to come forward.
